            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The Kanata Seniors’ Centre offers a wide range of recreation programs for adults aged 50 and over. Access to our services is through membership or program registration.</p>
<p>We are located at the rear of the <a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/facilities/place-listing/john-g-mlacak-centre">John&nbsp;Mlacak&nbsp;Centre</a>, which also includes an ice surface,&nbsp;Beaverbrook&nbsp;Library and the&nbsp;Kanata&nbsp;Civic Art Gallery. There is a convenient drop-off spot directly in front of the main entrance and parking lot to the side.</p>
</div>
      

